'''拉高德城堡'''（Château de la Gaude）是[[普罗旺斯地区艾克斯|普罗旺斯地区艾克斯]]的一个酒店，美食餐厅和商店。
==位置==
它位于普罗旺斯地区艾克斯的邦奇纳路（Route des Pinchinats）。<ref name="tourism">[http://en.aixenprovencetourism.com/aix-bastides.htm Aix-en-Provence official website: Bastides and Gardens] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103034927/http://en.aixenprovencetourism.com/aix-bastides.htm |date=2013-11-03 }}</ref><ref name="florence">Florence Signoret, Nils Solari, Liliane Counord, Gérard Bernar, ''Provence'',Le Petit Futé, 12008, p. 193 [https://books.google.com/books?id=rZp1jS5BStEC&pg=PA193&dq=%22Ch%C3%A2teau+de+la+Gaude%22+aix&hl=en&sa=X&ei=uOnAUvzfKdOFhQf0uYFQ&ved=0CE4Q6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=%22Ch%C3%A2teau%20de%20la%20Gaude%22%20aix&f=false]</ref><ref name="aynaud">Albert Aynaud, ''Aix-en-Provence, ses fontaines et leurs secrets'', 10, bd Roi-René, 1969, p. 184 [https://books.google.com/books?id=NsQjAAAAMAAJ&q=%22Ch%C3%A2teau+de+la+Gaude%22+aix&dq=%22Ch%C3%A2teau+de+la+Gaude%22+aix&hl=en&sa=X&ei=BO3AUoKkEYqihgf86oD4AQ&ved=0CFIQ6AEwBjgK]</ref><ref>Jean Pierre Babelon, ''Le Château en France'', Berger-Levrault, 1986, p. 312</ref><ref name="jeanpierre">Jean-Pierre Babelon, Jean-Baptiste Leroux, Mic Chamblas-Ploton, ''Jardins à la française'', Imprimerie Nationale, 1999, p. 283 [https://books.google.com/books?id=6uALAQAAMAAJ&q=%22Ch%C3%A2teau+de+la+Gaude%22+aix&dq=%22Ch%C3%A2teau+de+la+Gaude%22+aix&hl=en&sa=X&ei=7O7AUtftJ8mUhQeP14HIAQ&ved=0CDEQ6AEwADgU]</ref>，与另一座受保护的城堡[[米格纳德城堡|米格纳德城堡]]（Château de la Mignarde）处于同一条道路上，只是更北一些<ref name="aynaud"/><ref>Jean Paul Coste, Pierre Coste, ''La Provence'', PUF, 1977, p. 258</ref>。

==历史==
它建于18世纪<ref name="florence"/>，占地17[[公顷|公顷]]。<ref name="fute2008">Dominique Auzias, ''Aix-en-Provence: Pays aixois et salonais'', Le Petit Futé, 2008, p. 287 [https://books.google.com/books?id=QuMgNOGgBncC&pg=PA282&dq=%22Ch%C3%A2teau+de+la+Gaude%22+aix&hl=en&sa=X&ei=uOnAUvzfKdOFhQf0uYFQ&ved=0CDUQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=%22Ch%C3%A2teau%20de%20la%20Gaude%22%20aix&f=false]</ref> 楼高三层，车道两旁是栗树。<ref name="florence"/> 花园里有池塘、喷泉、带紫杉迷宫的园林、露台，甚至还有一条小径供捕猎蝴蝶。<ref name="florence"/> 此外，还有一个[[小圣堂|小圣堂]]。<ref name="lacaisse">''Les Monuments historiques de la France'', La Caisse nationale des monuments historiques, 1963, Volumes 9-10, p. 42 [https://books.google.com/books?id=xKOfAAAAMAAJ&q=%22Ch%C3%A2teau+de+la+Gaude%22+aix&dq=%22Ch%C3%A2teau+de+la+Gaude%22+aix&hl=en&sa=X&ei=7O7AUtftJ8mUhQeP14HIAQ&ved=0CEMQ6AEwAzgU]</ref> 庄园里还有葡萄园，出售葡萄酒<ref name="jeanpierre"/>。。

它归迪迪埃·布莱斯（Didier Blaise）所有<ref name="fute2008"/>。

==建筑==
1963年，该建筑列为[[法国历史遗迹|法国历史遗迹]]<ref name="lacaisse"/>。

